&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain a qualified pipeline of corporate prospects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the development of clear and consistent corporate engagement materials aligned with the Foundation’s public interest mandate&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to annual income planning and forecasting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor relevant corporate and capital market developments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Portfolio and relationship management&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
